---
layout: base.njk
title: Locations
breadcrumb: "Locations"
---

<p><em>The places you have walked, the cities you have changed, the ruins you may have caused.</em></p>

<div class="ornament">· · ·</div>

<div class="card-grid">
{% for location in collections.locations %}
  <a class="card" href="{{ location.url }}">
    <h3>{{ location.data.title }}</h3>
    {% if location.data.type %}<p>{{ location.data.type }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if location.data.region %}
    <span class="card-tag">{{ location.data.region }}</span>
    {% endif %}
  </a>
{% else %}
  <p><em>No locations recorded yet.</em></p>
{% endfor %}
</div>
